content.body:
Do `eval`/`Module`/`Function` on `new Evaluators()` get their intrinsics from the `globalThis` parameter? For example
```js
function MyArray() {}
const myGlobalThis = { Array: MyArray };
new Evaluators(myGlobalThis, importHook).eval("[]") instanceof MyArray; // ?
```

